  "body": "<div id=\"post-view221164043199\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea221164043199\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">안녕하세요&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이수한의원 소식 업데이트 하려구<span style=\"\">요&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">ㅋㅋ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">그동안 안녕하셨나요? ^^</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">지난 3주동안 우리한의원 건물에 이렇게</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">현수막이 걸려있었어요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7de5965af2159205.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:240px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjEg/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYxNzgy.4aOvoKbbl0TZKD8wNld5ENa_-aZFikJVEqkI3sezhBMg.FhldDCX-wvXB_5bjydw35RIgrArVN4s8lsn07wOwr2Eg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190905735.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7de5965af2159205.jpg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">그래서 아마도 이거 보고</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">한의원의 내부를 기대하는 분들이 더 많으실거같기도해요&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">기대하셔도 좋습니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ded52c373c2db614.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-2\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5fb01ed02871b3dd.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"427\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:427px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfODQg/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYxOTg4.63vjEnaFZ3esH_4n0o4UNKgNwmrPwXA-GvtNfuCknX4g.lec8F0y3wwSUwqizez3Jv56oL-wpf70bRSVcztfvwu8g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190905351.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5fb01ed02871b3dd.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">아 그리고</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">1층으로 들어오는 입구에&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">진료시간과 진료과목이 이렇게 한눈에 보이게 더 자세히 쓰여있습니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">그럼 지나가다가도 한번에 딱 보시겠죠?</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a7275a44e572f3a6.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"427\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:427px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjY4/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYyMTQ2.GgpGrXHCvLMcTQdyV8WFdYHtiAMT5pHv-_d9GvrYD9Mg.g2hHqfWXbbspFOZ1rhBJh1EXm7wCOHRzU1nVoNQpj-Ug.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190904912.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a7275a44e572f3a6.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">맨밑에 이수한의원 전화번도있으니</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">예약전화는 콜해주세요~&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ada8807bf1376880.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-2\"></a>&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">따르릉~</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5e40ea28d1a8774b.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:240px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTA4/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYyMzAw.AkqsZN7FUIhABUn8dbp_vZN_OQWMWlBnA9-uBUT30Wsg.TyE7OSOlOy6qhRQzRQ9tvk6_GdDAKZTInmcYV-ili0Ag.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190904610.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5e40ea28d1a8774b.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b940ad588fe5bb24.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:240px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjI3/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYyNDQy.VtxtnOAmDlVEwZKPs0XsYWi19whdpftwrAmKZwhCJA0g.eHRDVhpgpF5EyTYhRd9KCKssydHweHTZE3wfyvn7TpEg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190903720.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b940ad588fe5bb24.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14pt;\">일요일과 공휴일은 휴진</span></b>인거 잊지마시구요~ ^^</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">자.. 그리고</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">오늘 아침에 출근했을때는</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">청소 아주머니들께서 입주청소를 도와주고 계셨습니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2e27ddb26894c258.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"569\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:569px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfODcg/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYyNjI3.Gh14QHxHLA7FMHx82idKmqdaW-4hP4VEdccs6LzHdxkg.1q59DeccLbUmFkD4IaMVvhSZB2aqrf3ErAqaWNhnS_cg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190902135.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2e27ddb26894c258.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">깨끗하게 잘 청소 해주셨어요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">진짜</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span>창문이랑 벽이랑 바닥에 먼지 하나 없이 반짝반짝해요</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/860571df8a31087b.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"569\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:569px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTk1/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYyODAw.TlIVBhPnGmBbjY8yk_1rs3T9oRZlDcPNf_wkyKLqPm4g.fGnHGRT8mde4LhXPhkIzdYG4tDJXZvlXkUXUdf9KQ10g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190902456.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/860571df8a31087b.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">그럼 어떻게 변했나 한번 볼까요?&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">우선 입구부터 보시죠</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">유리문 드디어 작동됩니다</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c1385467e1fe0d7e.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTIg/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYyOTYw.Gd8ewA5bo6NxbCEaHZ-TsNuxhgrx-AW1PaFsQz4A_m0g.ZJIV5qRSa_HnEGu9Junx8-WfyACkgxRKfnHHI_FQKvYg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190846657.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c1385467e1fe0d7e.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">\"눌러주세요\" 버튼을 누루고 여니</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">적응이 안되네요&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">너무좋아요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c29010b370aa905f.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTA0/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYzMTU5.b-Xv29bKkInD1YsZb2nCJDMzU9hbvcJEXu9RDKdSSGog.JlrvL45GuXd_2bj48iJ5gcBAN8me0YhdQj0Ds0QMbwMg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190846093.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c29010b370aa905f.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">여기는 대기실이에요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">아직 소파가 안들어와서&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">창문이랑 정수기&nbsp;밖에없네요&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/be02ea513baf1cb6.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjQ1/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYzMzI3.NBa5dbugbTZIH9575xn7nz8VTR44NcaRSNQblu6u1FQg.Df8kca933vd5uPs2xzjdt8s11b96VQvlpa66-nSFTn8g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190847082.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/be02ea513baf1cb6.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이거는 블라인드를 내릴때 모습이구요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">우드 블라인드라 너무 멋있어요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">깔끔해서 좋네요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/149cca9442766806.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfNDQg/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYzNDQ3.c_fH3Y0PcBKh6tLKkW4tpHGTFXKx-1gki4kKeAlC-FEg.FwbHVsZezS9V_y8eeLri8eUvW3H1Cg5_7b_QYZoUIVAg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190845652.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/149cca9442766806.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">아 이수한의원은 환자분들의 안전을위해</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">대기실에는 시시티비 녹화중입니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7be985dceaeb0a07.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfNDEg/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYzNjU0.jDgg2x0c7Ij16gZNaJrVSxkr9nKP_WM-PUiRD3xmMP4g._nxc7Bo6fEW9V9_uRzKnbNdDCo_w3HKMhFypir2Syz4g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190842898.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7be985dceaeb0a07.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">짠~</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">여기는 데스크</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/67e0d86d277173aa.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTIx/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYzODMx.q-zl4jx50aj4_e8lnftVa_NleeoXdZdrPUXfSVaDVXog.Y8tA6KVj8nwMirjEz2NWPjlI7bMpOVdsCyoJB8WPL-cg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190847790.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/67e0d86d277173aa.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">너무 깔끔하죠?</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">저는 너무 좋아요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6904b90fe3ec59cb.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfNzIg/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjYzOTkx.jhcTI_DsaFSdfPGIws0oDEDPh0lLjVfu2JHahWWlFmcg.lbMcoshZNQgQSVXjwdFBQCrIpOocC-TBPhtp8oQN05gg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190848123.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6904b90fe3ec59cb.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">여기는 데기실에 티비 놓는자리</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/362f8046e97ac9c1.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTk5/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjY0MTM0.RV0gkdgn2q_FP5M5rkcPTIbYlC97bw3enrIu60vA3V4g.nah3Qj0oget6lwQFSc_yh3vkPyFB6ppMMxUTBF_JT-Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190847458.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/362f8046e97ac9c1.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">오른쪽으로 나원장님의 방이에요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">책상이랑 컴퓨터 의자 다 들어왔죠 오늘</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">아늑하니 좋아요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2f1102c0e92caf50.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTU4/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjY0MzM5.zX03067wGUs7cnoxliOL7PXKTdbqSq_Ri1RtK0BmEm0g.hbIl0qh1JPS12zrY2J1Y1xDk_r9eSNflhhisqVZ3fnUg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190845115.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2f1102c0e92caf50.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">나원장님 방의 놓을 부엉이 시계 입니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">소아과 이다 보니</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">아이들 컨셉에 맞춰 귀여운 부엉이 시계로 했어요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">잘어울리죠?</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4d118281794acddd.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjgx/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjY0Njgw.o3IyX4EjvSi6lbChzEvptzywytyRaEtG931_jJqjTOkg.pAPYTnGkKnFL-7GIavA91qMURcXHsZbU8hbfSA6E0Xgg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190902943.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4d118281794acddd.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">원장님 방에 놓을 보호자용 의자입니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">앉아보니 너무 편하고 좋더라구요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a6f2e2310996ccc1.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTY4/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjY0NTAx._0uvC4cgOpxFDicKXrwpXJrUDpXYnvS3MQMWW14DaLcg.P9NgdEEKN5o2ydCEp8C6mBUw5aLXs0Ig_IV9F0tk7ygg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190843904.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a6f2e2310996ccc1.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">여기서 부터는 치료실이에요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d09bf01068c8341a.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfNTEg/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjY0OTk4.OVOqAxAj2ttv_wKepbpf7sGyGaAg9PlwheV6IPTtcU0g.nuyElTu3l7aorJYxtwZDNIs7iuGYniz0nbdEUkxav2Ag.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190848499.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E677BBF')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d09bf01068c8341a.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/66326a0fb8dfe019.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjYx/MDAxNTEzMzM3MjY1MTk1.20FgqraBBKLuGXjdG_jtiTGxv6PwEvA4Ew6NXS0sm5Mg.r1eLShjd83fGeqgAKmRVZzr8h06gRDG